    <body>
      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="949A0852">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-949A0852-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A0852-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A0852-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">A <hi rend="italics">French</hi> G<hi rend="small-caps">ENTLEMAN</hi> dining with Company on a Fast-Day, called for some Bacon and Eggs. The rest were very angry, and reproved him for so heinous a Sin: Whereupon he wrote the following Lines, <hi rend="italics">Extempore</hi>, which are here translated.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-949A0852-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A0852-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A0852-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-949A0852-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A0852-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A0852-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial-italic">P<hi rend="italics">EUT on croire avec bon sens</hi></hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-2" n="2">Qu' un lardon le mit en colere;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-3" n="3">Ou, que manger un harang</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-4" n="4">C' est un secret pour luy plaire.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-5" n="5">En sa gloire envelopè</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-6" n="6">Songe t' il bien de nos soupè?</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-7" n="7"><lb/>In <hi rend="italics">English</hi>.__<hi rend="display-initial">W</hi>HO can believe, with common Sense,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-8" n="8">A Bacon Slice gives God Offence:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-9" n="9">Or, how a Herring hath a Charm</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-10" n="10">Almighty Anger to disarm.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-11" n="11">Wrapt up in Majesty divine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A0852-line-12" n="12">Does he regard on what we dine?</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
